QuestData.Title: Personal Property
QuestData.Description: You can detect no hinges or openings on this box. Were it not for the shifting of items inside, it could easily be mistaken for solid metal.$b$bIf anyone could know the method of its opening, it would be Highlord Mograine.
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring the Sealed Chest to Highlord Darion Mograine in Icecrown Citadel.
